  <summary date="2017-01-06T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Greater Grand Canyon Heritage National Monument Act

This bill establishes the Greater Grand Canyon Heritage National Monument in Arizona.

The Department of the Interior and the Department of Agriculture (USDA), with respect to lands under their respective jurisdictions, shall manage the Monument to conserve, protect, and enhance its natural resources and values.

Interior and USDA shall collaborate with the Greater Grand Canyon Heritage National Monument Advisory Council (established by this bill) to develop a plan for the protection and management of the Monument.</summary>
